sources.title: Final Days of an Icon: Romy Schneider (Biography) Full Documentary
sources.description:
The Final Days of Romy Schneider documentary offers an intimate portrayal of the actress during the twilight of her life, culminating in her passing on May 29, 1982, from cardiac arrest. It delves into the complexities of her personal struggles, the legacy she left behind, and the lasting impact of her untimely death on fans and the entertainment industry. Through poignant storytelling and rare insights, this documentary provides a tribute to Romy Schneider's enduring influence and talent.


This video has English, German & Russian audio options, and subtitled in many additional languages.

@CultCinemaClassics
